        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5063",
        "content": "And throwing strait their bows away, They grasp'd their swords so bright: And now sharp blows, a heavy shower, On shields and helmets light.]",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
