        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5063",
        "content": "This fight did last from breake of day Till setting of the sun; For when they rung the evening bell, The battel scarce was done.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
