        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5063",
        "content": "And the Lord Maxwell in like case Did with Erle Douglas dye; Of twenty hundred Scottish speres, Scarce fifty five did flye.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
