        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5063",
        "content": "\"Now God be with him,\" said our king, \"Sith it will noe better bee; I trust I have, within my realme, Five hundred as good as hee.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
